OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1773007876
OL,3,CWales win World Cup qualifier against
OL,4,CMontenegro with strong first-half show
OL,6,FIt was far more straightforward at
OL,7,FParc y Scarlets as Cain and Griffiths
OL,8,Fprovided a real attacking edge, with
OL,9,FRachel Rowe and Sophie Ingle helping
OL,10,Fto secure the second biggest win of
OL,11,FWilkinson's two-year reign.
OL,13,FMontenegro ` ranked 84 in the world
OL,14,Fand 52 places below Wales ` managed a
OL,15,Fsecond-half consolation as Armisa Kuc
OL,16,Fdeprived the hosts of a first clean
OL,17,Fsheet in 17 games.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
