FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1773007876
OL,3,CWales win World Cup qualifier against
OL,4,CMontenegro with strong first-half show
OL,6,FWales were fortunate to avoid
OL,7,Fembarrassment after just 55 seconds
OL,8,Fwhen Safia Middleton-Patel took too
OL,9,Flong to clear a back pass from
OL,10,FRhiannon Roberts.
OL,12,FThe Manchester United goalkeeper's
OL,13,Fkick was charged down by Medina Desic
OL,14,Fbut fell the wrong side of a post as
OL,15,Ffar as Montenegro were
OL,16,Fconcerned.Wales' scoring spree began
OL,17,Fafter six minutes when Cain raced on
OL,18,Fto Ceri Holland's through-ball and
OL,19,Fslotted in to an inviting gap at the
OL,20,Fnear post.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
