PN,46404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1773007876
OL,3,CWales win World Cup qualifier against
OL,4,CMontenegro with strong first-half show
OL,6,FCain turned provider to set up the
OL,7,Funmarked Rowe and Griffiths, making
OL,8,Fher first competitive start, added a
OL,9,Fthird after 17 minutes following some
OL,10,Fhesitant goalkeeping from Ajsa Kalac.
OL,12,FMontenegro escaped when Cain hit a
OL,13,Fpost, but Ingle soon met Mia Ross'
OL,14,Fcross from close range.
OL,16,FWales made it five after 35 minutes as
OL,17,FLily Woodham broke down the left and
OL,18,Fsquared for Cain to tap home with the
OL,19,FMontenegro defence absent again.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
