FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1773007876
OL,3,CWales win World Cup qualifier against
OL,4,CMontenegro with strong first-half show
OL,6,FAt that stage Wales were scoring at a
OL,7,Frate to get them close to their record
OL,8,Ftally, the 15-0 victory over
OL,9,FAzerbaijan in 2010.
OL,11,FBut Montenegro sent on Maja Saranovic
OL,12,Fto shore up a ragged backline and it
OL,13,Fbecame more of an even contest.
OL,15,FHome hopes of a first clean sheet
OL,16,Fsince a Euro 2025 play-offs victory
OL,17,Fover Slovakia vanished five minutes
OL,18,Fafter the restart.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
