PN,46406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1773007876
OL,3,CWales win World Cup qualifier against
OL,4,CMontenegro with strong first-half show
OL,6,FJasna Djokovic floated a free-kick
OL,7,Fbeyond the Wales defence, and Kuc got
OL,8,Fthere first to lob the ball over
OL,9,FMiddleton-Patel and into an empty net.
OL,11,FGriffiths turned 19 on Tuesday and the
OL,12,FManchester United striker, currently
OL,13,Fon loan at Sunderland, had more cause
OL,14,Ffor belated birthday celebrations
OL,15,Fafter rounding Kalac from Carrie
OL,16,FJones' through-ball.
OL,18,FWales return to World Cup action with
OL,19,Fa double-header against Albania next
OL,20,Fmonth.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/6
